ZH: 这朵蓝色的花将很快开花。
EN: This blue flower will bloom soon.

ZH: 春天到了，各种花都开始开花了。
EN: Spring has arrived, and all kinds of flowers are starting to bloom.

ZH: 大约15天后，这种植物将开花。
EN: Approximately 15 days later, this plant will blossom.

ZH: 这座公园里有很多漂亮的花儿开花了。
EN: Many beautiful flowers have bloomed in this park.

ZH: 他们种植了许多种类的花，每种都在不同的季节开花。
EN: They have planted many types of flowers, each blooming in different seasons.

ZH: 那些樱花树已经开始开花了。
EN: Those cherry blossom trees have already started blooming.

ZH: 昨天晚上下雨了，可能会影响花朵开花的时间。
EN: It rained last night, which may affect the timing of the flowers blooming.

ZH: 我们去看看那些罂粟花在云雾中盛开的花朵。
EN: Let's go see those poppy flowers blooming in the mist.

ZH: 我今天早上沐浴在花香中，因为我的花已经开始开花了。
EN: I bathed in the fragrance of flowers this morning because my flowers have started blooming.

ZH: 高山上的野花也在这个季节开始开花了。
EN: Wildflowers on the mountain also start blooming in this season.

ZH: 这棵树的花还没有开花。
EN: The flowers on this tree have not bloomed yet.

ZH: 葡萄藤终于在这个夏天开花了。
EN: The grapevines have finally bloomed this summer.

ZH: 这些向日葵因为充足的阳光而迅速开花。
EN: These sunflowers are blooming quickly due to ample sunlight.

ZH: 我们所有人都在等待那些玫瑰花开花。
EN: All of us are waiting for those roses to bloom.

ZH: 这种植物每年都开花两次。
EN: This plant blooms twice every year.

ZH: 你必须定时浇水才能让植物开花。
EN: You have to water the plants regularly to help them bloom.

ZH: 水仙花通常在春季开花。
EN: Daffodils usually bloom in the spring.

ZH: 昨天我们看到了一朵大玫瑰绽放。
EN: We saw a big rose bloom yesterday.

ZH: 这种花在夜晚盛开，呈现出迷人的光景。
EN: These flowers bloom at night, presenting a charming sight.

ZH: 随着天气变暖，室内植物开始开花。
EN: With the weather getting warmer, indoor plants are starting to bloom.
